  <description><![CDATA[<p>The hotel exterior looks like your standard traditional Alpine hotel, but step inside and the interior combines what you’d expect together with colourful, retro décor reflecting the owner’s vibrant personalities. The Brandl-Berger family and their team take a lot of personal pride in making sure you have everything you need whilst you stay with them. Located perfectly right in the middle of <a data-udi="umb://document/0096e5e76c954be2b2a6b43d386098c6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0096e5e76c954be2b2a6b43d386098c6}" title="Saalbach">Saalbach’s</a> lively resort centre and just a few minutes’ walk to a few different lifts, is another great plus point. Weekly music night with the resident Elvis impersonator is a must.</p>]]></description>
